2026-05-15T21:11:21.4800550Z 249            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4800830Z 250            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4801094Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4801365Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4801542Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4801834Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4802092Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T21:11:21.4802498Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
